PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to a previous conviction on the</hi> 19<hi rend="italic">th August,</hi> 1867, <hi rend="italic">at this Court</hi>—(<hi rend="italic">Sentence deferred, he being a witness against Markham and Gill.—See Old Court, Saturday</hi>).</p>
